Create a landing page for any product/CV/project
- call for action buttons - at least 3 (CALL US/REGISTER/CLICK)
- at least 4 sections
- at least 5 images
- 1 page only (index.html)
- css, js and img folders
- readable fonts
- header and footer with copyrights and contact information (not necessary to be real)
- embedded video from youtube
Project requirements:
Link to a git repository (10 pts max) it should have readme.md with a link to web-site, description and some screenshots (use github pages)
JavaScript events (clicker and random Fetch API things) - (10 pts max)
Design that is responsive (10 pts max)
Performance test passed (10 pts max)
Custom CSS with several classes and id's with style for div element (10 pts max)
Clean and Valid code (10 pts max)
